location app build with nodejs and react.
to run in debug mode:  
    for the client -> yarn start
    server -> yarn run dev
directory structure:
client -> client app
    src
        api-> backend integration
        components -> react ui components
        constanst -> constants
server -> server
    db-> migrations and seed
    src 
        router -> express endpoints
        services -> controller and repository
        models -> knex model schema
        middlewares -> error handling middlewares
        index.ts -> main.app

to start the application:
    make build
    make up
to remove images:
    make clean